'''亞速爾群島航空'''（Azores Airlines）是一家以[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[亞速爾群島|亞速爾群島]]作為根據地的航空公司，總部位於[[聖米格爾島|聖米格爾島]]的[[蓬塔德爾加達|蓬塔德爾加達]]市<ref>"[http://www.sata.pt/sites/default/files/BrochuraSATA_2014_net_4.pdf The Atlantic and You] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SBKmcgJZ?url=http://www.sata.pt/sites/default/files/BrochuraSATA_2014_net_4.pdf |date=20140829052126 |dateformat=iso }}" (Company Brochure) (). SATA International. Retrieved on August 29, 2014. p. 19/19. "GRUPO SATA Sede | Headoffice: Av. Infante D. Henrique nº55 9504-528 Ponta Delgada S.Miguel – Açores"</ref><ref>"[http://www.sata.pt/sites/default/files/PRESS%20KIT.MAR%C3%87O%20%202010_en_L2_0.pdf Press Kit 2010] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sata.pt/sites/default/files/PRESS%20KIT.MAR%C3%87O%20%202010_en_L2_0.pdf |date=20130604201656 }}." SATA. Retrieved on 7 July 2010. "The SATA Group comprises air transport companies whose decision centre is located in the city of Ponta Delgada, on the island of São Miguel, in the archipelago of Azores."</ref>，並以聖米格爾島的{{link-en|若望·保禄二世机场|João Paulo II Airport}}作為樞紐。為{{link-en|SATA亞速爾群島航空|SATA Air Açores}}的子公司。

==航點==
亞速爾群島航空主要連結[[亞速爾群島|亞速爾群島]]與[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]本土、[[北美|北美]]、[[維德角|維德角]]等地。詳細可參見{{link-en|亞速爾群島航空航點列表|List of Azores Airlines destinations}}。

